The Prestige;;92;;76;;PG-13;;An illusion gone horribly wrong pits two 19th-century magicians, Alfred Borden (Christian Bale) and Rupert Angier (Hugh Jackman), against each other in a bitter battle for supremacy. Terrible consequences loom when the pair escalate their feud, each seeking not just to outwit -- but to destroy -- the other man.;;Drama,Fantasy,Mystery & thriller;;Christopher Nolan;;2006;;Hugh Jackman,Christian Bale,Michael Caine,Scarlett Johansson,Piper Perabo,Rebecca Hall,David Bowie,Samantha Mahurin,Andy Serkis,Rob Arbogast,Chris Cleveland,Edward Hibbert,Jamie Harris,William Morgan Sheppard,Jim Piddock;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/prestige